      "id": "PopularPost328724",
      "post_content": "The creature can still block unless its black. This card isn't bad, its decent against black decks, but its also not so good that people would sideboard it as black hate (Sounds racist), and most people avoid maindecking cards that are mostly for use against one color unless they are *really* excellent. (See some of the counterspell hate out there)  \n  \nStill, since no attacking is the main effect of pacifism, you could argue for its use. White doesn't get too many cantrips.",
